Check : pseudocode
Skill-building Activity
1. To check positive or negative
Get number
IF the number is greater than 0
PRINT “Positive”
ELSE
PRINT “ Negative”
ENDIF

2. To check odd or even number
Get n
IF n is divisible by 2
PRINT “Even”
ELSE
PRINT “Odd”
ENDIF
3.To check greatest of three numbers
READ a,b,c
IF a is greater than b, and a is greater than c
PRINT “ a is greatest”
IF b is greater than a, and b is greater than c
PRINT “ b is greatest”
IF c is greater than a, and c is greater than b
PRINT “c is greatest”
ELSE
PRINT “yay”
ENDIF
